msgid "Only admins can demote members."
msgstr "관리자만 멤버를 강등할 수 있습니다."

#: apps/circles/views.py:677
msgid "Only moderators can be demoted."
msgstr "중재자만 강등할 수 있습니다."

#: apps/circles/views.py:684
#, python-format
msgid "%(name)s demoted to member."
msgstr "%(name)s이(가) 멤버로 강등되었습니다."

#: apps/circles/views.py:703
msgid "Only admins and moderators can remove members."
msgstr "관리자와 중재자만 멤버를 삭제할 수 있습니다."

#: apps/circles/views.py:714
msgid "Cannot remove an admin."
msgstr "관리자를 삭제할 수 없습니다."

#: apps/circles/views.py:719
